WEBVTT

00:00:00.151 --> 00:00:03.558
The bedrock of all effective leadership is self-awareness.

00:00:04.460 --> 00:00:12.636
Before leading a global matrix organization, it is necessary to be intimately aware of internal cognitive and emotional architecture.

00:00:13.418 --> 00:00:21.293
Consciousness of self is the ability to acknowledge internal thoughts, feelings, and reactions, as well as external behaviors.
